flowchart TD
    A([User taps push notification\nor opens app directly]) --> B{Valid session\ntoken in Keychain?}
    B -->|No| C[Display Sign In screen\nUC-001]
    C --> D[User authenticates\nApple or Google]
    D --> E{Auth\nsuccess?}
    E -->|No| F[Display error:\nSign in failed — try again]
    F --> C
    E -->|Yes| G[Store new session token\nin iOS Keychain]
    B -->|Yes| H[Read user city from\nlast known location]
    G --> H
    H --> I{City\nknown?}
    I -->|No — location not granted| J[Show city selector prompt\nor request location permission UC-002]
    J --> K[User selects or confirms city]
    K --> L[Fetch this week's spot from Firebase\nvia Backend Service]
    I -->|Yes| L
    L --> M{Spot found\nfor current week?}
    M -->|No| N[Display: Check back Thursday\nfor this week's spot]
    N --> O[Show most recent historical spot\nas context if available]
    O --> P[Fetch 4-week history\nUC-010]
    M -->|Yes| Q[Display spot detail screen:\nname · address · photo · hours · description]
    Q --> P
    P --> R{History\nreturned?}
    R -->|Firebase timeout or error| S[Display cached history\nwith Last updated label]
    S --> T[Fetch social signals:\ncheckin count · friend visit count UC-006]
    R -->|Success| U[Display 4-week history\nscrollable card stack below spot]
    U --> T
    T --> V{Social signals\nreturned?}
    V -->|Error| W[Show checkin count as 0\nno friend breakdown]
    V -->|Success| X[Display inline:\nX people checked in · Y friends]
    W --> Y[Display I'm Here button\nif user is near venue UC-007]
    X --> Y
    Y --> Z([Spot detail screen fully loaded])
